name: Unfinished Super Rare Mixtape Jam 1 Submission
name_original: Unfinished Super Rare Mixtape Jam 1 Submission
description:
Left / Right arrow keys to turn, 

WASD to move.

Space to use lightning.

Left CTRL to use rockets.

Unfortunately I ran out of time to finish this, the university work at the moment is overwhelming, which is sad. I hope you like what there is though. Hopefully there will be enough time with the next jam.

Made in love2d using Pyram3d Tools.
